question: List all ETPs and UITs where the exit fee is 0.01.
sql_query1:
SELECT Products.Name 
FROM Products
WHERE (Products.Category = "ETP" OR Products.Category = "UIT") AND Products.ExitFee = 0.01
sql_query2:
SELECT Products.Name 
FROM Products
WHERE Products.Category = "ETP" OR Products.Category = "UIT" AND Products.ExitFee = 0.01
interpretation1: List all entries for both ETPs and UITs where the exit fee is 0.01.
interpretation2: Show all the ETP records, in addition show the UIT records with an exit fee of 0.01.
